</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>E38-5 (TAM) - E38-13 (SG-2)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Ignition switch on (IG) at 25°C (77°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
